      • lbr_gru

        public static final dnnl.algorithm lbr_gru
        GRU cell with linear before reset. Differs from the vanilla GRU in how the new memory gate is calculated: c_t = tanh(W_c*x_t + b_{c_x} + r_t*(U_c*h_{t-1}+b_{c_h})) LRB GRU expects 4 bias tensors on input: [b_{u}, b_{r}, b_{c_x}, b_{c_h}]
